6088141\" width=630 height=210 /></span><br>•车身定制：<br>用控制论植入物和增强的实验室培养器官替换身体部位以获得特殊能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/8013d278a52b809a145e07d718dba834.poster.avif?t=1766088141\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/8013d278a52b809a145e07d718dba834.webm?t=1766088141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/8013d278a52b809a145e07d718dba834.mp4?t=1766088141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>•动态敌人：<br>憎恶有固定的行为，你可以研究，但随着游戏的进行，它们获得了相互融合的能力，产生了具有增强力量的可怕怪物。",
